Package org.freeinternals.format.classfile.attribute

Class RuntimeTypeAnnotations.type_annotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.freeinternals.commonlib.core.FileComponent
      • org.freeinternals.format.classfile.attribute.RuntimeTypeAnnotations.type_annotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenerateTreeNodeFileFormat, GenerateTreeNodeClassFile
    Enclosing class:
    RuntimeTypeAnnotations
    public static class RuntimeTypeAnnotations.type_annotation
extends FileComponent
implements GenerateTreeNodeClassFile
    The type_annotation structure has the following format. 
     type_annotation {
   u1 target_type;
   union {
     type_parameter_target;
     supertype_target;
     type_parameter_bound_target;
     empty_target;
     formal_parameter_target;
     throws_target;
     localvar_target;
     catch_target;
     offset_target;
     type_argument_target;
   } target_info;
   type_path target_path;

   u2        type_index;
   u2        num_element_value_pairs;
   {   u2            element_name_index;
       element_value value;
   } element_value_pairs[num_element_value_pairs];
 }
